Financial education website that aims to explain complex financial concepts and events in simple language for teens and kids. Our mission is to cure the growing problem of financial illiteracy in America by providing the future workforce with the skills to make their futures financially secure.

- Write articles every 2 weeks

projects.name: Terminal All In One
projects.description:
- A VS Code extension that builds on top of the default integrated terminal with scripts, themes, commands, and keybindings.
- Built with the VS Code API and TypeScript. Mocha used for testing. Travis CI used for the CI pipeline.
- GitHub Repository: https://github.com/YashTotale/terminal-all-in-one
